OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FVideo report by Katie Oscroft
OL,8,FAn asylum seeker who was inside a
OL,9,Fhotel when it was attacked by a mob of
OL,10,Frioters has told ITV News that he
OL,11,Fthought he was going to be "burned
OL,12,Falive."
OL,14,FAli - not his real name - was in the
OL,15,FHoliday Inn Express in Wath-upon-
OL,16,FDearne, near Rotherham, when hundreds
OL,17,Fof protesters who gathered outside
OL,18,Fthrew missiles and tried to set fire
OL,19,Fto the building on 4 August.
