OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FAli said he is still "traumatised" by
OL,7,Fthe events of that day.
OL,9,F"When I saw smoke, we were all inside
OL,10,Fand we thought we will be burned alive
OL,11,F- sometimes when I am asleep I see
OL,12,Fthis again," he said.
OL,14,F"We heard them smash windows with
OL,15,Fbricks. They threw missiles - we heard
OL,16,Fsuch a noise.JIf it wasn't for the
OL,17,Fpolice we would have died."
