OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FSixty-four police officers, three
OL,7,Fpolice horses and a police dog were
OL,8,Finjured during the disorder.
OL,10,FAli said he thought he was going to
OL,11,Fdie.
OL,13,FHe said: "I thought I would never see
OL,14,Fmy family again. We smelled the smoke
OL,15,Fand we didn't want to be inside but
OL,16,Fthey smashed windows... It was many
OL,17,Fpeople, so we daren't go outside."
OL,19,F"Thank you to the police because we
OL,20,Fwould be dead if they hadn't helped us.
