OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,F"I saw with my own eyes a policeman
OL,7,Flying on the floor hurt. And a female
OL,8,Fpolice (officer). God bless them."
OL,10,FAli, who has been moved to a different
OL,11,Flocation since the disorder, said that
OL,12,Fhe would not feel safe to return to
OL,13,FRotherham.
OL,15,F"I would like people like this to
OL,16,Flearn about us - we are not so
OL,17,Fdifferent. I know some people, asylum
OL,18,Fseekers, do bad things but not most
OL,19,Fpeople."
