OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police said 118 people
OL,7,Fhave been arrested over the disorder
OL,8,Fso far while 33 people have been
OL,9,Fsentenced.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, 4 September, a 13-year-
OL,12,Fold boy became the youngest person to
OL,13,Fbe convicted over the trouble outside
OL,14,Fthe South Yorkshire hotel.
OL,16,FThe court heard that the teenager had
OL,17,Fthrown a lit firework and stones at
OL,18,Fpolice guarding the hotel.
